                     <interp inst="t18370814-1836-offence-1" type="offenceSubcategory" value="simpleLarceny"></interp> for stealing, on the <rs id="t18370814-cd-61" type="crimeDate">
                        <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t18370814-1836-offence-1 t18370814-cd-61"></join>12th of July</rs> 2 pewter-pots, value 1<hi rend="italic">s</hi>., 6<hi rend="italic">d</hi>. the goods of <persName id="t18370814-name-475" type="victimName">
